Items.c: “終於有了新突破！翅膀高舉的鷹像可以用於開啟通道,將此事刻於此處或許能幫到下一個摔至山谷下的人。”
Items.mt: "Finally, a new breakthrough! The eagle with its wings held high can be used to open the passage, and carving this here may help the next person who falls down the valley."
